      model: "gemini-3-flash-preview",
      contents: `Generate a coding challenge task for a student learning Object-Oriented Programming in ${language}. 
      The task should involve writing a class or a set of classes/methods. 
      Keep it focused on intermediate concepts like inheritance, polymorphism, or encapsulation.`,
